# Esiana Roadmap Context

Source: [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/Esiana-ttrpg/esiana-core/issues) and [Milestones](https://github.com/Esiana-ttrpg/esiana-core/milestones) (last reviewed 2026-06-15).

## Status

- **Shipped:** v1.0.1
- **In progress:** Post-1.0 views and plugins over frozen schema

## Before implementing roadmap work

1. Check open [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/Esiana-ttrpg/esiana-core/issues) and current Milestones
2. Prefer extending shipped primitives over greenfield rewrites
3. Check [deferred-backlog.md](../../docs/deferred-backlog.md) for deferred, `won't-do`, or `plugin-only` items

## Do not assume shipped (near-term open)

- Layer 6 narrative intelligence (session prep, pacing analytics)
- Map atlas polish (clustering, cached manifests) — core atlas shipped

## Shipped pre-1.0 audit (2026-06-13)

- Cross-system fog/revelation (L1–4 complete)
- OpenAPI `/api/docs` (version-locked in core); human API/plugin docs in [`docs/`](../../docs/) wiki
- See [pre-1.0-export-audit.md](../../docs/audits/pre-1.0-export-audit.md), [migration-audit.md](../../docs/audits/migration-audit.md)

